                    .column.is-12
                        = image_tag "https://nicolada-website.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/oc-display.webp", class: "display", loading: 'lazy'
                    .column.is-4
                        = image_tag "https://nicolada-website.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/oc-dangler.webp", class: "pop", loading: 'lazy'
                    .column.is-4
                        = image_tag "https://nicolada-website.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/wobbler-oc2.webp", class: "pop", loading: 'lazy'
                    .column.is-4
                        = image_tag "https://nicolada-website.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/wobbler-oc.webp", class: "pop", loading: 'lazy'
                .project-details__description-wrapper
                    .columns.is-variable.is-6
                        .column.is-4
                            %p.eyebrow Strategy
                            %h2 Influencers
                        .column.is-8
                            %p.projects__middle-text
                                Alongside the offline efforts, we proposed an influencer program centered around people whose content naturally aligned with the product, whether that was wellness, food, or lifestyle. The goal was to spark genuine interest and encourage people to try it out rather than just see an ad. We also proposed reaching out to media figures and holistic health influencers as part of a broader PR push, and designed a media kit that would include two Ocean Spray Chilled Juices, a recipe book, and a personalized tag, all packaged in a tote bag.
                .columns.is-multiline
                    .column.is-4
                        .project-details__img-wrapper
                            = image_tag "https://nicolada-website.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/oc-cup.webp", class: "cup gallery__media", loading: 'lazy'
                    .column.is-4
