                .project-details__description-wrapper
                    .columns.is-variable.is-6
                        .column.is-4
                            %p.eyebrow Strategy
                            %h2 Sales Bundle
                        .column.is-8
                            %p.projects__middle-text
                                To push product trials even further, we proposed a partnership with RonPon, a popular virtual liquor store in Puerto Rico. The idea was to include a sample of Chilled Juice along with a recipe flyer and product info in every order. It was a low-pressure way to introduce the product to new consumers while giving them something useful and a little unexpected.
