                        .column.is-4
                            %p.eyebrow Strategy
                            %h2 Social Media
                        .column.is-8
                            %p.projects__middle-text
                                For social media, we proposed content that felt relevant and easy to connect with rather than overly salesy. The plan was to highlight the health benefits like 100% daily Vitamin C and the antioxidant properties of cranberries, but frame them in a way that fit naturally into everyday conversations about wellness. We also proposed leaning into the growing trend of skinny drinks, positioning Chilled Juice as the perfect base for cocktails and mocktails. The idea was to bridge the gap between a health-conscious beverage and something fun, speaking to people who want to enjoy life without compromising on what they put in their body.
